data.description: Become the new owner of this beautiful and spacious 2 story home located in a very desirable neighborhood in West Palmdale, close to everything. Property offers 4 beds, 2.5 baths, a huge entertainment room upstairs,  tank less water heater , Wireless Lutron Smart system installed which can easily be controlled from your phone, 3 car garage. No HOA.
